Upper & Lower case transfer:

UPPER(field name) UPPER(string) 

LOWER ( character_expression )  

CONCAT ( string_value1, string_value2 [, string_valueN ] )  

LEFT ( string , integer )  i.e. LEFT('abcdefg',2) 'ab'

RIGHT ( string , integer ) 

SPACE(integer)  #n space

TRANSLATE('2*[3+4]/{7-2}', '[]{}', '()()')      i.e. 2*(3+4)/(7-2)

RTRIM('Removes trailing spaces.   ')           i.e.'Removes trailing spaces.'

TRIM( '     test    ')            or                 TRIM( '.,! ' FROM  '#     test    .')

STRING_SPLIT ( string , separator )

SUBSTRING('abcdef', 2, 3)       'bcd'

STUFF('abcdef', 2, 3, 'ijklmn')         i.e. replacement aijklmnef 



wildcard:
 
*   Represents zero or more characters     bl* finds bl, black, blue, and blob
?   Represents a single character          h?t finds hot, hat, and hit
[]  Represents any single character within the brackets     h[oa]t finds hot and hat, but not hit
!   Represents any character not in the brackets      h[!oa]t finds hit, but not hot and hat
-   Represents a range of characters        c[a-b]t finds cat and cbt
#   Represents any single numeric character       2#5 finds 205, 215, 225, 235, 245, 255, 265, 275, 285, and 295
%   Represents zero or more characters          bl% finds bl, black, blue, and blob
_   Represents a single character         h_t finds hot, hat, and hit
^   Represents any character not in the brackets        h[^oa]t finds hit, but not hot and hat


